  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even then the-- all the clean bricks with that-- a hammer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the Polish Christians, they used to come with their horses and their wagon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to-- we have to load the bricks and take it to the train to-- to send it to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the good part of it was there, we was around the rubbles-- the rubble from the-- from the fall down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a-- we find there, like, silver spoons, silver-- silver knives, sometimes gold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- and-- and the Polacks that-- the Christian Polacks that-- we start talking to them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We ask 'em, you wanna-- you wanna a spoon, a silver spoon?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He who goes into the city, he could go and sell it for a much higher price-- but to Warsaw, if he it goes out from the gate, from the thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So bring me a bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they-- they-- they help us to combine our feedback, you know, it was-- they're changing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were finding whatever, digging there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were-- and I-- we would blow the thing, find the spoon-- silver, whatever we can.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They give-- they give us a salami, bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were doing business with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So little by little, I started getting back to my-- my strength.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The only thing that was wrong with me, I was to have no food to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Besides that, I was very healthy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but in the beginning, I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we got there, we got-- from the filth and everything, we had no water, no everything-- the lice was coming on top of us like a-- like an army-- going all over, even inside the food.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
